Lunexia on Osu! 07/04/2022 5:54 PM
Usually, this setup is what we call "feedbackless". This means that you don't learn of being roleblocked. The only exception is the Tracker, who should receive "No Result" instead of "Did not visit" or "Visited [name]", at least that is how it is usually run! (Nash may run this differently, in which case it's best to ask him in directly) The same applies to someone being protected, no feedback is given, neither to the attacker, protector nor protected. The only role that gets feedback in this setup is the Tracker and only for its own abilities results. And well, you will know if you died or not. (edited)
